room_title: Escape room "Dumbledore: The Quest" by Escape Rooms Portland Michigan in Lansing
room_description: The time has come to defeat the Dark Lord but there is still another object that Dumbledore has instructed you to retrieve. The problem is, you don't know where it is and the "bad guys" are on their way. You are locked into Dumbledore's office until you find the item and get it out safely! Can you make it out before the Dark Lord and his followers get to it first?
